videos.headline: Iowa's Caitlin Clark erupts for 35 points in win vs. Kentucky
videos.description: Iowa freshman Caitlin Clark goes off for 35 points as she leads the Hawkeyes to an 86-72 win over Kentucky in the second round of the tournament.
